room_title: Escape room "The Rabbit Hole: Welcome to 221B!" by Down the Rabbit Hole in Tucson
room_description: In this room, you have entered Sherlock’s Flat! The first item you notice is a letter from Scotland Yard. Holmes appears to be the latest victim in a string of crimes sweeping through London. While sifting through clues and using your deductive reasoning, you will unravel a story like no other. Follow the clues, unlock Sherlock’s most hidden secret, and find out how and why he met his demise.
